oai_dc:dc.dc:description: This conference was sponsored jointly by the Council on Wave Research, Berkeley, California, and the Rijkswaterstaat, of the Netherlands. Dean Morrough P. O'Brien is Chairman of the Council on Wave Research and Mr. A. G Maris is Director - General of the Rijkswaterstaat. Mr. J B Schijf, Chief Engineer-Director of the Rijkswaterstaat, acted as secretary of the conference. Appreciation is expressed to the Rijkswaterstaat for photographs supplied to illustrate the cover and the section title pages of this publication.
